<h1 >痔</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" href="/view/10812319.htm" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
</dd>
</dl><span class="view-tip-panel">
<a class="viewTip-icon" href="/subview/71844/10028254.htm" target="_blank" title="同义词">同义词</a>
<span class="viewTip-fromTitle">痔疮</span>一般指痔
</span>
<div class="authorityListPrompt">
<div class="main-content-zj">
本词条由<a href="http://www.baikemy.com/" target="_blank" class="nslog:7140">国家卫健委权威医学科普项目传播网络平台/百科名医网</a>
提供内容
。</div>
</div>
<div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">痔（俗称<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE/201198" data-lemmaid="201198">痔疮</a>）是一种位于肛门部位的常见疾病，任何年龄都可发病，但随着年龄增长，发病率逐渐增高。在我国，痔是最常见的肛肠疾病。</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="poster-middle">
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div></div>
<div class="poster-bottom">
<div class="baseBox notDouble hasVideoAndFocus mr-30">
<div class="dl-baseinfo">
<dl class="">
<dt>别称</dt>
<dd title="痔疮">
痔疮
</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="">
<dt>英文名称</dt>
<dd title="hemorrhoid">
hemorrhoid
</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="">
<dt>就诊科室</dt>
<dd title="外科">
外科
</dd>
</dl>
<dl class="bottomLine">
<dt>常见发病</dt>
<dd title="肛门">
肛门
</dd>
</dl>
</div>
</div>
<dl class="lemmaWgt-guideCard mr-30">
<dt class="title">专家解读</dt>
<dd class="detail">
<a id="medical_goTab" class="medical_goTab" href="javascript:;" title="点击查看‘科普文章’" _tabIndex="me_articleTab">
<div class="docHeadPic">
<img height="94" src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/h%3D94/sign=73197fd30d7b020813c933e562d98814/b8389b504fc2d562982a879be01190ef76c66ca1.jpg" alt="专家图片">
</div>
<div class="re_desTitle">
<h4 class="desTitleH4" title="我们该如何来区别直肠癌和痔疮">我们该如何来区别直肠癌和痔疮</h4>
<p class="desText" title="二者发病部位相似，最常见的症状都为便血，因此更要注意二者间的鉴别诊断。">二者发病部位相似，最常见的症状都为便血，因此更要注意二者间的鉴别诊断。</p>
<em class="docIco docIcoArticle"></em>
</div>
</a>
</dd>
</dl>
</div>
</div>
